Leading research projects and directing junior staff


Creating advanced quantitative models


Screening of cutting edge academic literature and interacting with leading academics in quantitative modelling


Identification of new, valuable datasets outside of Deutsche Börse Group


Presentation of results/models/data to internal service line and clients


Working with service line product development to support productization of the IP


